      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、このお仕事が終わったら忘年会だよね\nみんなスケジュール合わせて、寮に集まるって聞いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日は、このお仕事が終わったら忘年会だよね\nみんなスケジュール合わせて、寮に集まるって聞いてる",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……そうなんだ、今から胃が痛いよ……\n思ったよりも大がかりになっていてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うぅ……そうなんだ、今から胃が痛いよ……\n思ったよりも大がかりになっていてな……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.4359166782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……胃、大丈夫？\nそんなに、緊張する……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……胃、大丈夫？\nそんなに、緊張する……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1770963033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、な\nまぁ、年に一回の余興だし……大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そりゃあ、な\nまぁ、年に一回の余興だし……大丈夫だよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0262115638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね……今日の特番、頑張るから、見てて\nアイドルとして、ちゃんと自信のある姿を見せるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えっとね……今日の特番、頑張るから、見てて\nアイドルとして、ちゃんと自信のある姿を見せるから",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3569601695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.8707252662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
