      "text": "雫……そうか、そうだよな\n現役アイドルのお墨付きだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "雫……そうか、そうだよな\n現役アイドルのお墨付きだったな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
